 1) What is the most important tool for adding colors to certain areas of the page rather than the entire background ?
ans::table


2) Which of the following is NOT a valid pair for browser safe colors ?
ans::AA


3) Adding a border to your image helps the visitor to recognize it as what ?
ans::a link


4) Why should you specify a background color if you are using an image for the actual background of your page ?
ans::  The background color will be shown until the image loads


5) What is used to store information usually relevant to browsers and searchengines?
ans:: Metatags


6) Why should you add alternative text to your images ?
ans:: So the users can get an idea of what the image is before it loads
